Minors:
- WARNING! In accordance with European Union (EU) Legislation,
  all minors who are nationals of New Caledonia will be
  expected to hold their own passport or National ID Card
  (where applicable) when departing from Bulgaria, Croatia,
  Cyprus, Romania or a Schengen Member State . 
Additional Information:
- Visitors are required to hold all documents required for
  their next destination.
Warning:
- Passengers not holding proof of means of onward travel could
  be refused entry.
 - Exempt are holders of a General Entry Permit (GEP). 
 - Exempt are holders of a Temporary Entry Permit (TEP)
   endorsed with a ticket waiver.
